This paper deals with detecting the semantic types of data columns in relational tables, which is a task related to data preparation, schema matching, data discovery, and semantic search. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
